        </div>
    </div>
</div>
                        
                        <p>While there was general doubt about whether the honor code solved the problem of dishonesty, many agreed that it is important for an academic institution to take a stand on issues of cheating, regardless of its ability to deter violators. "I think an honor code is just a statement for the school," Sid Palani said.</p>

